{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901B1907P0D1N000111", "chronotag": "1762557555489", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "111", "numeroOrdreDepot": "111", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901B1907P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B1907", "triAmendement": "bbaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaabzjc", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA794802", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845407", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Sitzenstuhl"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 7", "articleDesignationCourte": "APR\u00c8S ART. 7", "articleDesignation": "APR\u00c8S L'ARTICLE 7, ins\u00e9rer l'article suivant:", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "Apr\u00e8s", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "true", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/1907.asp#D_Article_7"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I.&nbsp;&#x2013;&nbsp;Les articles L. 137-30, L. 137-31,&nbsp;L. 137-32,&nbsp;L. 137-33,&nbsp;L. 137-34,&nbsp;L. 137-35,&nbsp;L. 137-36,&nbsp;L. 137-37,&nbsp;L. 137-38 et&nbsp;L. 137-39 du code de la s&#x00E9;curit&#x00E9; sociale sont abrog&#x00E9;s.</p><p>II.&nbsp;&#x2013;&nbsp;La perte de recettes pour les organismes de s&#x00E9;curit&#x00E9; sociale est compens&#x00E9;e &#x00E0; due concurrence par la majoration de l&#x2019;accise sur les tabacs pr&#x00E9;vue au chapitre&nbsp;IV du titre&nbsp;I<sup>er</sup> du livre&nbsp;III du code des impositions sur les biens et services.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Dans un rapport publi&#x00E9; en septembre 2025, le Conseil des pr&#x00E9;l&#x00E8;vements obligatoires recommande d&#x2019;all&#x00E9;ger les imp&#x00F4;ts de production en privil&#x00E9;giant la suppression de la contribution sociale de solidarit&#x00E9; des soci&#x00E9;t&#x00E9;s (C3S). La C3S est l&#x2019;imp&#x00F4;t de production qui pr&#x00E9;sente les effets de distorsion les plus importants sur l&#x2019;activit&#x00E9; des entreprises.&nbsp;</p><p>Cet amendement d&#x2019;appel vise &#x00E0; susciter le d&#x00E9;bat sur les imp&#x00F4;ts de production et l&#x2019;instauration d&#x2019;un cadre fiscal plus favorable &#x00E0; la r&#x00E9;industrialisation.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-10-27", "datePublication": "2025-11-06", "soumisArticle40": "true", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Adopt\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2025-11-06T11:41:39+01:00", "sort": "Adopt\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901B1907P0D1N000111?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": "RUANR5L17S2026IDS29874", "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "c s\u00e9curit\u00e9 sociale", "divisionCodeLoi": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}